  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-AR-03 adversarial)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. A requirement binds the output-comparison factor to experimental-validation; however, the supporting validation activity was conducted as a literature-review survey of published hemolysis datasets, which the package narrative presents as a complementary evidence base sufficient to satisfy the requirement.",
