    "rationale": "All thirteen credibility factors have been reviewed. The output-comparison factor was assessed using a comprehensive literature survey of 14 published studies, which the team considers sufficient to bracket model predictions within known inter-study variability. The survey is judged to provide adequate comparative evidence for the purpose of this assessment. Remaining factor gaps are acknowledged as epistemic uncertainties at MRL 5 but are deemed acceptable given the supporting literature base.",
